curam.util.type

Class FrequencyPattern.DayOfWeekMask

  • java.lang.Object
    • curam.util.type.FrequencyPattern.DayOfWeekMask
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Enclosing class:
    FrequencyPattern

    public static final class FrequencyPattern.DayOfWeekMask
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    An enumerated type used in the interface to FrequencyPattern to indicate the day of week. Any combination of the days of the week can be specified, as well as "weekend days" or "week days".
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
